EventItemActionName: Hearing on P-C Item by Comm
EventItemActionText: This Communication was Hearing on P-C Item by Comm
EventItemTitle: Pursuant to ยง3-212(e) of the New York City Administrative Code, the Council of the City of New York and the Mayor are empowered to jointly appoint five members to serve on the New York City Lobbying Commission.  In addition, the Council and the Mayor jointly designate a Chair from among the Commission members.  The Council will consider the appointment of Herbert Berman as a member of the New York City Lobbying Commission and consider his designation as Chair.  If appointed, in conjunction with the Mayor, Mr. Berman will serve an undefined term.
